% \subsection{The \cn{substack} command}
%
%    The \cn{substack} command can be used to set subscripts
%    and superscripts that consist of several lines. Usage:
% \begin{verbatim}
% X_{\substack{a=1\\b=2}}
% \end{verbatim}
